channel.title: My Router Is Hard To PortForward
channel.description:
My router is WRT54G made by Linksys. My friends say this is a very hard Router to portforward, I agree with them. Can someone give me step-by-step directions fer this? My MSN messenger is charriotscape@hotmail.com. I could send you a link for the default guide if you need one.
Thanks, The Keeper
